OL,3,C#400m rail testing facility 'delayed
OL,4,Cfor five years'
OL,6,FA state of the art rail testing
OL,7,Ffacility near Ystradgynlais is at
OL,8,Fleast five years behind schedule, it
OL,9,Fhas been revealed.
OL,11,FOn Friday, Powys County Council
OL,12,Fcouncillors received a report
OL,13,Foutlining the risks to the council
OL,14,Fassociated with transforming the
OL,15,Fformer Nant Helen opencast mine and
OL,16,FOnllwyn washery site into a Global
OL,17,FCentre of Railway Excellence (GCRE).
