OL,3,C#400m rail testing facility 'delayed
OL,4,Cfor five years'
OL,6,FThe development has a potential to
OL,7,Fcreate hundreds of jobs and could
OL,8,Frevitalise the economy bringing in an
OL,9,Festimated #300 million into the area.
OL,11,FThe GRCE - estimated to cost #400m to
OL,12,Fdevelop - would allow testing for new
OL,13,Ftrain and track technologies.
OL,15,FThe committee were told by director of
OL,16,Feconomic development and growth Diane
OL,17,FReynolds that further planning
OL,18,Fapplications from GCRE for the site
OL,19,Fwere expected to be submitted next
OL,20,Fyear.
