OL,6,FPlanning permission which agreed the
OL,7,Fprinciple of developing the site were
OL,8,Fagreed by both Powys and Neath Port
OL,9,FTalbot council planning committees
OL,10,Fback in 2021.
OL,12,FLast year GCRE had an application to
OL,13,Fextend the timescale allowed to
OL,14,Fprovide detailed plans for the
OL,15,Ffacility, approved by planners.
OL,17,FThe Welsh Government first revealed
OL,18,Fplans for the site back in 2018, and
OL,19,Fit was originally expected that the
OL,20,Fsite would be operational by 2025.
