OL,6,FMs Reynolds explained: "These things
OL,7,Fchange over time they are looking to
OL,8,Fput in a revised planning
OL,9,Fapplications."
OL,11,FFuture proposals would include
OL,12,Frestoring a footpath that goes around
OL,13,Fthe edge which could form part of a
OL,14,Fcycle way.
OL,16,F"I think they are looking at improving
OL,17,Faccess as well," said Ms Reynolds.
