OL,6,FCommittee vice-chairman and lay member
OL,7,FJohn Brautigam said: "There is a risk
OL,8,Fstated in the report that there is a
OL,9,Fskills deficit for the jobs that would
OL,10,Fbe needed there.
OL,12,F"What is being done about that?"
OL,14,FMs Reynolds said: "The GCRE have a
OL,15,Fhuge programme to entice people into
OL,16,Fengineering."
