OL,6,F"They have been doing STEM (Science,
OL,7,FTechnology, Engineering, and
OL,8,FMathematics) sessions with Year Six
OL,9,Fpupils going out to all of the local
OL,10,Fschools providing training and getting
OL,11,Fyoung people interested in the types
OL,12,Fof skills that will be needed for the
OL,13,Ffuture running of such a site.
OL,15,F"We don't expect the site to be up and
OL,16,Frunning until 2030 so we're talking
OL,17,Ffive years.
